<section class="advanced-demo blur-demo" aria-label="失焦、拖影和慢门示意图">
  <div class="advanced-demo__grid">
    <div class="advanced-demo__card">
      <div class="advanced-demo__badge">失焦</div>
      <div class="advanced-demo__scene blur-demo__scene blur-demo__scene--defocus">
        <div class="blur-demo__shape blur-demo__shape--near">记忆</div>
        <div class="blur-demo__shape blur-demo__shape--far">人物</div>
        <div class="blur-demo__focus-ring">焦点偏开</div>
      </div>
      <p>失焦不是拍坏，而是把信息从“看清是谁”转到“感觉发生了什么”。关键是主体关系还要能被读到。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="advanced-demo__card">
      <div class="advanced-demo__badge">慢门拖影</div>
      <div class="advanced-demo__scene blur-demo__scene blur-demo__scene--motion">
        <div class="blur-demo__light blur-demo__light--one"></div>
        <div class="blur-demo__light blur-demo__light--two"></div>
        <div class="blur-demo__walker">人影</div>
      </div>
      <p>慢门把时间压进一张照片里。人物不完全清楚、灯线拖开、边缘漂浮，都会让画面像一段模糊记忆。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
